snippet.title: Sangrur ਵਿੱਚ ਪ੍ਰਦਰਸ਼ਨਕਾਰੀਆਂ ਉੱਤੇ ਪੁਲਿਸ ਕਾਰਵਾਈ, EX CM Channi ਵੀ ਰੋਕੇ ਗਏ | 𝐁𝐁𝐂 𝐏𝐔𝐍𝐉𝐀𝐁𝐈
snippet.description:
ਕਾਰਕੁਨ ਭਾਨਾ ਸਿੱਧੂ ’ਤੇ ਦਰਜ ਪੁਲਿਸ ਕੇਸਾਂ ਦੇ ਵਿਰੋਧ ’ਚ ਮੁੱਖ ਮੰਤਰੀ ਦੀ ਸੰਗਰੂਰ ਰਿਹਾਇਸ਼ ਘੇਰਨ ਜਾ ਰਹੇ ਪ੍ਰਦਰਸ਼ਨਕਾਰੀਆਂ ਨੂੰ ਸ਼ਨੀਵਾਰ ਨੂੰ ਕਈ ਥਾਵਾਂ ਉੱਤੇ ਰੋਕਿਆ ਗਿਆ। ਇਸ ਦੌਰਾਨ ਸੀਐੱਮ ਭਗਵੰਤ ਮਾਨ ਦੀ ਰਿਹਾਇਸ ਵੱਲ ਵੱਧ ਰਹੇ ਕਿਸਾਨਾਂ, ਨੌਜਵਾਨਾਂ ਤੇ ਸਿਆਸੀ ਪਾਰਟੀਆਂ ਨੂੰ ਕਾਰਕੁਨਾਂ ਦੀ ਪੁਲਿਸ ਨਾਲ ਤਕਰਾਰ ਵੀ ਹੋਈ। ਦੂਜੇ ਪਾਸੇ ਪੰਜਾਬ ਦੇ ਸਾਬਕਾ ਮੁੱਖ ਮੰਤਰੀ ਚਰਨਜੀਤ ਸਿੰਘ ਚੰਨੀ ਨੇ ਵੀ ਇਲਜ਼ਾਮ ਲਗਾਇਆ ਕਿ ਪੁਲਿਸ ਨੇ ਉਹਨਾਂ ਨੂੰ ਸੰਗਰੂਰ ਜਾਣ ਤੋਂ ਰੋਕਿਆ ਹੈ।
ਰਿਪੋਰਟ- ਕੁਲਵੀਰ ਸਿੰਘ, ਐਡਿਟ- ਗੁਰਕਿਰਤਪਾਲ ਸਿੰਘ

localized.title: Sangrur ਵਿੱਚ ਪ੍ਰਦਰਸ਼ਨਕਾਰੀਆਂ ਉੱਤੇ ਪੁਲਿਸ ਕਾਰਵਾਈ, EX CM Channi ਵੀ ਰੋਕੇ ਗਏ | 𝐁𝐁𝐂 𝐏𝐔𝐍𝐉𝐀𝐁𝐈
localized.description:
ਕਾਰਕੁਨ ਭਾਨਾ ਸਿੱਧੂ ’ਤੇ ਦਰਜ ਪੁਲਿਸ ਕੇਸਾਂ ਦੇ ਵਿਰੋਧ ’ਚ ਮੁੱਖ ਮੰਤਰੀ ਦੀ ਸੰਗਰੂਰ ਰਿਹਾਇਸ਼ ਘੇਰਨ ਜਾ ਰਹੇ ਪ੍ਰਦਰਸ਼ਨਕਾਰੀਆਂ ਨੂੰ ਸ਼ਨੀਵਾਰ ਨੂੰ ਕਈ ਥਾਵਾਂ ਉੱਤੇ ਰੋਕਿਆ ਗਿਆ। ਇਸ ਦੌਰਾਨ ਸੀਐੱਮ ਭਗਵੰਤ ਮਾਨ ਦੀ ਰਿਹਾਇਸ ਵੱਲ ਵੱਧ ਰਹੇ ਕਿਸਾਨਾਂ, ਨੌਜਵਾਨਾਂ ਤੇ ਸਿਆਸੀ ਪਾਰਟੀਆਂ ਨੂੰ ਕਾਰਕੁਨਾਂ ਦੀ ਪੁਲਿਸ ਨਾਲ ਤਕਰਾਰ ਵੀ ਹੋਈ। ਦੂਜੇ ਪਾਸੇ ਪੰਜਾਬ ਦੇ ਸਾਬਕਾ ਮੁੱਖ ਮੰਤਰੀ ਚਰਨਜੀਤ ਸਿੰਘ ਚੰਨੀ ਨੇ ਵੀ ਇਲਜ਼ਾਮ ਲਗਾਇਆ ਕਿ ਪੁਲਿਸ ਨੇ ਉਹਨਾਂ ਨੂੰ ਸੰਗਰੂਰ ਜਾਣ ਤੋਂ ਰੋਕਿਆ ਹੈ।
ਰਿਪੋਰਟ- ਕੁਲਵੀਰ ਸਿੰਘ, ਐਡਿਟ- ਗੁਰਕਿਰਤਪਾਲ ਸਿੰਘ
#protest #punjab

snippet.description:
The Budget countdown begins! Catch the most credible, non-stop coverage of the interim budget on CNBC-TV18 | Budget Live | CNBC Awaaz LIVE
🔴 Stock Market Updates Live | Budget 2024 Live Updates : आज कहां करें Invest | Stock Market live updates | Share Market Live | Business & Finance | 01 Feb  | Stock Market News | Interim Budget 2024 LIVE
Business News Live | First Trade में जानें बजट के दिन कैसा है Market का हाल, बाजार खुलने के बाद कहां बन रहा है कमाई का अच्छा मौका. जानें किन Stocks में Intraday में दिख रहा है अच्छी कमाई का मौका. रहें First Trade में हर छोटी-बड़ी मार्केट की खबर से जागरुक. देखिए बजट से जुड़ी हर अपडेट सबसे पहले लाइव. 

Budget 2024 LIVE: This year's budget is ‘interim’ in nature as the government is set to face a general election in April-May this year. Union finance minister Nirmala Sitharaman is slated to present the financial year 2024-25 budget on February 1. This will be the final annual financial statement of the BJP-led PM Narendra Modi government's second term. Last week, the traditional pre-budget ‘halwa’ ceremony was held, initiating a ‘lock-in’ period for officials involved in budget preparation to maintain confident. "There is a fragrance of 'Ek Bharat Shreshth Bharat' here, and it also carries the consciousness of India's civilisation and culture. This also has the pledge to honour democratic and cultural traditions, and a resolve to build new traditions of new India of 21st century," President Murmu said.

snippet.title: Rakesh Barot | પ્રેમ તારો મારો | Prem Taro Maro | Gujarati Romantic Song 2024 | નવું ગુજરાતી ગીત
snippet.description:
રાકેશ બારોટ એક મધુર રોમેટિક ગુજરાતી ગીત સાથે પાછા ફર્યા છે - પ્રેમ તારો મારો માત્ર @SaregamaGujarati  પર

Title: Prem Taro Maro
Producer: Red velvet cinema 
Singer : Rakesh Barot
Artist : Rakesh Barot,Hiral Patel
Child Artist :Aliya Nai
Co Artist : Ratilal,Bhudev thara
Music: Mayur Nadiya
Lyrics: Vipul Raval
Creative Producer : Dhyey Films & Team
Edit : Naresh Rajput
Makeup: Chirag Parmar
Hair : Kinjal Raval
Dop :Sehazad Mansuri (Tipu)
Concept: Purvi Vasava ,Faruk Gayakwad
Director : Faruk Gayakwad
Production : Mahesh Prajapati 
Technical Support: Jenish Talaviya 
Spe.Thanks :Parbatbhai okhapura

Lyrics:
પોની રે સેવાળ જેવો પ્રેમ તારો મારો
એ પોણી રે સેવાળ જેવો પ્રેમ તારો મારો (૨)
એ આજ યાદ કરીને રડતો મારે નથી  હથવારો
એ તને પરણા પછી મોઢું જોયું નથી તારું
એક તું મને સાચવતી આજ નથી કોઈ મારું

ગામ ભગોળે ભેગા થતા(૨)
અરે ગોમ ભગોડે ભેગા થતા લાગતો તને પ્યારો 
એ તું વાતો કરતા થાકતી નહીં મારે બોલવાનો ના વાળો એ પોની સેવાડ જેવો હતો પ્રેમ તારો મારો

હો ઉદાસ મારું દિલ આજે તારા વગર રડતુ
તું હતી ત્યારે સુખ હતું આજ દુઃખ ચાલ્યું  છે વધતું 
હું હંભરાય તારા ભણકારા ઊંઘ માંથી જાગી જવ છું
તારી ચિંતા મને ચિંતામાં હું અડધો થઈ જાઉં છું
હું તને કે તારા પ્રેમને રાકેશ ભૂલુ નહી હું ક્યારેય એવું કહેવા વાળી આજે નથી મારી હારે
સાથ નહીં છોડુ એવો (૨)
સાથ નહીં છોડુ એવો આલતી મને સહારો
હે ચમ મજબૂર થઈને પરણી નથી મળવાનો મારો વારો
એ પાણી સેવાડ જેવો હતો પ્રેમ તારો મારો
હે તારા વગર અંગે અંગમાં લાગી મને આગ રે
સુકાઈ ગયો પ્રેમ પારલો લીલો મારો વાડ રે 
હે વિખરાઈ ગયો આખો પ્રેમ નો મારો  માળો
તારી બળતરામાં મારો જાતો નથી દહાડો
એ ક્યારે  ભેતાળો તારો પાસે થાશે એ જાણે મારો રોમ
મારા દિલને તારું ભુલાશે નહી નોમ
સાથે રે જીવવાનો(૨)
સાથે રે જીવવાનો હોય લેખ તારો મારો
મને આખી જિંદગી નહીં ભુલાશે પ્રેમ તારો મારો 
હે પોણી સેવાડ જેવો હતો પ્રેમ તારો મારો 
હે આજ યાદ કરીને રડતો મારો નથી હક વાળો 
હે પોની સેવાડ જેવો હતો પ્રેમ તારો મારો

#rakeshbarot 
#saregamagujarati 
#gujaratisong 
#newgujaratisong 
#gujaratisong2024

રાકેશ બારોટ એક મધુર રોમેટિક ગુજરાતી ગીત સાથે પાછા ફર્યા છે - પ્રેમ તારો મારો માત્ર @SaregamaGujarati  પર

Title: Prem Taro Maro
Producer: Red velvet cinema 
Singer : Rakesh Barot
Artist : Rakesh Barot,Hiral Patel
Child Artist :Aliya Nai
Co Artist : Ratilal,Bhudev thara
Music: Mayur Nadiya
Lyrics: Vipul Raval
Creative Producer : Dhyey Films & Team
Edit : Naresh Rajput
Makeup: Chirag Parmar
Hair : Kinjal Raval
Dop :Sehazad Mansuri (Tipu)
Concept: Purvi Vasava ,Faruk Gayakwad
Director : Faruk Gayakwad
Production : Mahesh Prajapati 
Technical Support: Jenish Talaviya 
Spe.Thanks :Parbatbhai okhapura

Lyrics:
પોની રે સેવાળ જેવો પ્રેમ તારો મારો
એ પોણી રે સેવાળ જેવો પ્રેમ તારો મારો (૨)
એ આજ યાદ કરીને રડતો મારે નથી  હથવારો
એ તને પરણા પછી મોઢું જોયું નથી તારું
એક તું મને સાચવતી આજ નથી કોઈ મારું

ગામ ભગોળે ભેગા થતા(૨)
અરે ગોમ ભગોડે ભેગા થતા લાગતો તને પ્યારો 
એ તું વાતો કરતા થાકતી નહીં મારે બોલવાનો ના વાળો એ પોની સેવાડ જેવો હતો પ્રેમ તારો મારો

હો ઉદાસ મારું દિલ આજે તારા વગર રડતુ
તું હતી ત્યારે સુખ હતું આજ દુઃખ ચાલ્યું  છે વધતું 
હું હંભરાય તારા ભણકારા ઊંઘ માંથી જાગી જવ છું
તારી ચિંતા મને ચિંતામાં હું અડધો થઈ જાઉં છું
હું તને કે તારા પ્રેમને રાકેશ ભૂલુ નહી હું ક્યારેય એવું કહેવા વાળી આજે નથી મારી હારે
સાથ નહીં છોડુ એવો (૨)
સાથ નહીં છોડુ એવો આલતી મને સહારો
હે ચમ મજબૂર થઈને પરણી નથી મળવાનો મારો વારો
એ પાણી સેવાડ જેવો હતો પ્રેમ તારો મારો
હે તારા વગર અંગે અંગમાં લાગી મને આગ રે
સુકાઈ ગયો પ્રેમ પારલો લીલો મારો વાડ રે 
હે વિખરાઈ ગયો આખો પ્રેમ નો મારો  માળો
તારી બળતરામાં મારો જાતો નથી દહાડો
એ ક્યારે  ભેતાળો તારો પાસે થાશે એ જાણે મારો રોમ
મારા દિલને તારું ભુલાશે નહી નોમ
સાથે રે જીવવાનો(૨)
સાથે રે જીવવાનો હોય લેખ તારો મારો
મને આખી જિંદગી નહીં ભુલાશે પ્રેમ તારો મારો 
હે પોણી સેવાડ જેવો હતો પ્રેમ તારો મારો 
હે આજ યાદ કરીને રડતો મારો નથી હક વાળો 
હે પોની સેવાડ જેવો હતો પ્રેમ તારો મારો

snippet.title: क्यों घेर रखा है गुंडों ने Taarak को? | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Revisit The Journey
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

Some strange people come inside the Gokuldham society and demand money for the festivals. Daya, Komal, and Babita are buying vegetables and encounter them on the way. They start asking each and every one a large sum of money as donations. 

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 435
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2024 #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

snippet.title: Udaariyaan | उड़ारियां | Ep. 949 | Aasma की Alia से मदद की पुकार | Latest Update
snippet.description:
Aasma ने Alia को Phone कर मांगी Armaan के लिए मदद, Armaan की आज़ादी के लिए Aasma ने Begum Sahiba के आगे रखी शर्त

-------------------

🌟 Embark on a Heartwarming Journey with Udaariyaan: Dreams Take Flight! 🌟

Welcome to the captivating world of 'Udaariyaan,' where dreams soar high against the rustic backdrop of a quaint village in Punjab. Join the spirited Sandhu family as they set out on an extraordinary quest to bid adieu to their beloved sarson ke khet and embrace the land of dreams, Canada, fondly known as Kaneda! 🌾🍁🏞️

In this exhilarating tale, fate weaves an unexpected twist, introducing us to the two vibrant sisters, Tejo and Jasmine. Their lives take an enthralling turn when the charming and dashing Fateh walks into their lives, leaving them with heart-pounding emotions and unforeseen challenges. 💓😍🤩

Will these three souls unite their dreams and take flight towards their cherished sapon ki Udaariyaan? Will they overcome the hurdles that destiny throws their way? Experience a rollercoaster of emotions, laughter, and love as you follow their enthralling journey towards making their dreams a reality. 🎢🎭💖

Subscribe now and don't miss a single moment of 'Udaariyaan' - a show that will tug at your heartstrings, leaving you inspired and cheering for every triumph and tribulation along the way. 🌈✨

🎬 Watch 'Udaariyaan' every week and witness the magic unfold! 📺🎉
🔗 Follow us for more updates, exclusive clips, and behind-the-scenes moments! 📲🎥

snippet.title: Wrath of Salaar | Music By Ravi Basrur | Hombale Films
snippet.description:
Witness the vengeance, feel the power - Wrath of Salaar 

From the Makers of  "KGF: Chapter 1 & 2," &  the visionary director Prashanth Neel, comes a film that will push the boundaries of cinematic brilliance, presenting you the First Single of "Salaar", featuring the powerhouse talents of Prabhas, Prithviraj, Shruthi Haasan, Tinu Anand, Eshwari Rao, Jagapathi Babu, Sriya Reddy, Garuda Ram.  
Brace yourself for an extraordinary tale of rebellion filled with power-packed action and impactful music by Ravi Basrur. 
Rebel Star Prabhas shines as Salaar, Directed by Prasanth Neel, and produced by Hombale Films.
 
Get Ready to Rebel with us and witness the most violent man on screens this Dec 22, 2023.

snippet.title: Year of the Azure Dragon | Clash of Clans Lunar New Year
snippet.description:
The Year of the Azure Dragon symbolizes strength & power. This season brings both, with Dragon skins and a special event! Happy Lunar New Year!



Follow us on our Socials!
Twitter ► https://twitter.com/ClashofClans/
Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/clashofclans 
Facebook ► https://www.facebook.com/ClashofClans 
TikTok ► https://www.tiktok.com/@clashofclans

Attack. Defend. Strategize. Download for free for mobile devices. supr.cl/PlayClashOfClans

From rage-­filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/

Privacy Policy:
https://supercell.com/en/privacy-policy/

Terms of Service:
https://supercell.com/en/terms-of-service/

https://supercell.com/en/parents/

snippet.title: ABORTION-ന് ശേഷം ഇരയായി മാറുകയായിരുന്നു| @ammakkili | Josh Talks Malayalam
snippet.description:
#joshtalksmalayalam #ammakkili #survivor 
പഠിച്ചുകൊണ്ട് വളരൂ ജോഷ് Talks-ലൂടെ- നിങ്ങളുടെ Communication Skills മെച്ചപ്പെടുത്താൻ, ജോഷ് ടോക്സിന്റെ Malayalam to English app-ൽ ചേരുക: ‌https://joshskills.app.link/QRSpMrLudGb 

കുഞ്ഞുണ്ടാകാൻ വൈകിയാൽ മച്ചി വിളികൾ കേൾക്കുന്നവർ നമുക്ക് ചുറ്റിനും ഇപ്പോഴുമുണ്ട്. കുഞ്ഞുണ്ടായ ശേഷം പാലുകൊടുക്കാൻ കഴിഞ്ഞില്ലെങ്കിലോ? അവിടെയും ആ സ്ത്രീ ഒരു ഇര തന്നെ ആകുന്നു. പത്തനംത്തിട്ട സ്വദേശിയായ ജിൻസിയുടെ അനുഭവമാണിത്. #cancer  വലിഞ്ഞുമുറുകുമ്പോഴും ചുറ്റിനും കേട്ടുകൊണ്ടിരുന്ന കുറ്റപ്പെടുത്തലുകളാണ് തളർച്ച കൂട്ടിയത്. ഇന്നിതാ തന്റെയും കുടുംബത്തിന്റെയും വളർച്ചയിൽ മുഖ്യ പങ്ക് ജിൻസിയ്ക്കുണ്ട്. #ammakkili  #youtubechannel -ന്റെ കൂടി ഉടമയാണ് ഇന്നത്തെ ജിൻസി. ഏതൊരു പെൺകുട്ടിയ്ക്കും, സ്ത്രീയ്ക്കും, അമ്മമാർക്കും ഇന്നത്തെ ടോക്ക് പ്രചോദനമേകും. ടോക്ക് കാണാം.    

In today's episode of Josh Talks Malayalam on our channel, we are privileged to have Jincy, a renowned #youtuber  and #survivor , as our guest speaker. Jincy's channel, #ammakkili , has gained immense popularity for its inspiring content, and today, she shares her incredible journey with us. Jincy has faced multiple challenges in her life, including pregnancy complications and breast cancer, but she has emerged victorious through her sheer determination and positivity. Her story is an inspiration for all those who are going through similar struggles in life, reminding us that we too can overcome our obstacles with courage and hopefulness like Jincy did! Tune into our channel now to hear Jincy's inspiring story and learn how she transformed her life through her unwavering spirit! 

ഇപ്പോൾ നിങ്ങൾക്ക് Josh Talks വീഡിയോകളിൽ നിങ്ങളുടെ ബ്രാൻഡ് പ്രദർശിപ്പിക്കാനും പരസ്യം ചെയ്യാനും varun@joshtalks.com- ഇൽ Connect ചെയ്യൂ.

If you find this talk helpful, please like and share it and let us know in the comments box.
You can now showcase and advertise your brand on the Josh Talks videos, reach out to us at varun@joshtalks.com, if you are interested.

Josh Talks passionately believes that a well-told story has the power to reshape attitudes, lives, and ultimately, the world. We are on a mission to find and showcase the best motivational stories from across India through documented videos and live events held all over the country. Josh Talks Malayalam caters to the Malayalam speaking audience worldwide. It aims to inspire and motivate Malayali's by showcasing Malayalam motivation through the experiences of fellow Malayali's. Josh talks Malayalam and brings to you the best Malayalam motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women’s rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 9 languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the setbacks they face in their career and helping them discover their true calling in life.

ജോഷ് Talks ഇന്ത്യയിലെ ഏറ്റവും പ്രേരണാത്മകമായ കഥകൾ ശേഖരിക്കുകയും അവ പങ്കുവെക്കാൻ ഒരു വേദി നൽകുകയും ചെയ്യുന്നു. വിവിധ പശ്ചാത്തലങ്ങളിൽ നിന്നുള്ള അനുഭവസ്ഥർ, അവരുടെ സംഘർഷഭരിത കഥകൾ പങ്കുവയ്ക്കുന്നു. ചെറുതായി തുടങ്ങിയ ജോഷ് Talks, നിലവിൽ 9 ഭാഷകളിൽ കഥകൾ പങ്കുവയ്ക്കുന്നു. ഊർജ്ജസ്വലരായ യുവജനങ്ങളുടെ കഴിവുകളെ പ്രോത്സാഹിപ്പിക്കുകയും, അവരുടെ ജീവിതത്തിൽ  നേരിടുന്ന തിരിച്ചടികൾ മറികടക്കാൻ അവർക്ക് പ്രചോദനം നൽകുകയും ചെയ്യുക എന്നതാണ് ഞങ്ങളുടെ ലക്ഷ്യം.
#worldcancerday #cancersurvivor #pregnancy

snippet.title: Goodbye KOZHENCHERRY 😔 Shifting to our new Home in Kochi | ജന്മനാട്ടിൽ നിന്നും കൊച്ചിയിലേക്ക്‌
snippet.description:
Goodbye KOZHENCHERRY 😔 Shifting to our new Home in Kochi | ജന്മനാട്ടിൽ നിന്നും കൊച്ചിയിലേക്ക്‌ #techtraveleat #kozhencherry 

വീഡിയോയിൽ കാണിക്കുന്ന കൊച്ചിയിൽ ഞങ്ങൾ താമസിച്ച വീടിന്റെ കൂടുതൽ വിവരങ്ങൾക്ക് : +919846687667, 9037617615.
https://abnb.me/a7cbZCmzNGb

Our own house where Abhi and I was born and brought up at Kozhencherry. We are going to shift from that house to Ernakulam. Now we are getting ready to live in a new place. You can see our process of shifting from Kozhencherry to Ernakulam in this video.

ഞാനും അഭിയുമെല്ലാം ജനിച്ചു വളർന്ന കോഴഞ്ചേരിയിലെ ഞങ്ങളുടെ സ്വന്തം വീട്. അവിടെ നിന്നും എറണാകുളത്തേക്ക് ഞങ്ങൾ മാറിത്താമസിക്കുകയാണ്. പുതിയ സ്ഥലത്തെ ജീവിതം തുടങ്ങുവാനുള്ള തയ്യാറെടുപ്പുകൾ തുടങ്ങുകയാണ്. കോഴഞ്ചേരിയിൽ നിന്നും ഫാമിലിയുമായി എറണാകുളത്തേക്ക് മാറുന്ന വിശേഷങ്ങളാണ് ഈ വീഡിയോയിൽ.

Goodbye KOZHENCHERRY 😔 Shifting to our new Home in Kochi | ജന്മനാട്ടിൽ നിന്നും കൊച്ചിയിലേക്ക്‌ #techtraveleat #kozhencherry 

വീഡിയോയിൽ കാണിക്കുന്ന കൊച്ചിയിൽ ഞങ്ങൾ താമസിച്ച വീടിന്റെ കൂടുതൽ വിവരങ്ങൾക്ക് : +919846687667, 9037617615.
https://abnb.me/a7cbZCmzNGb

Our own house where Abhi and I was born and brought up at Kozhencherry. We are going to shift from that house to Ernakulam. Now we are getting ready to live in a new place. You can see our process of shifting from Kozhencherry to Ernakulam in this video.

ഞാനും അഭിയുമെല്ലാം ജനിച്ചു വളർന്ന കോഴഞ്ചേരിയിലെ ഞങ്ങളുടെ സ്വന്തം വീട്. അവിടെ നിന്നും എറണാകുളത്തേക്ക് ഞങ്ങൾ മാറിത്താമസിക്കുകയാണ്. പുതിയ സ്ഥലത്തെ ജീവിതം തുടങ്ങുവാനുള്ള തയ്യാറെടുപ്പുകൾ തുടങ്ങുകയാണ്. കോഴഞ്ചേരിയിൽ നിന്നും ഫാമിലിയുമായി എറണാകുളത്തേക്ക് മാറുന്ന വിശേഷങ്ങളാണ് ഈ വീഡിയോയിൽ.

Episode 3998: Permanent Number Ka Celebration
--------------------------------------------------------
Sodhi shares sweets with everyone in Gokuldham to celebrate getting the permanent number for his new car. A patient visits Dr Hathi complaining about a loss of taste. Later, Sodhi and Tapu Sena decide to have a party together. 

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3998, 3 Feb 2024
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: RBI Bans PayTM in INDIA | PayTM FASTag, Wallet, UPI Going To Close After 29th Feb 2024 | SidTalk
snippet.description:
Hey Guys,
In this video you'll get to know that RBI bans PayTM Payments Bank & Its services like: PayTM UPI, PayTM Wallet, PayTM FASTag, NCMC Card, Prepaid Cards, etc.
Other paytm service: PayTM QR, POS Machine, Soundbox, Payment Gateway will work?
Action against Paytm Payments Bank Ltd under Section 35A of the Banking Regulation Act, 1949
Explained: Why RBI Has Put Restrictions On Paytm Payments Bank
Common question by PayTM customers:
My NCMC Card will stop working?,
My POS Machine/Soundbox not work?,
My Fast Tag will stop working?

PayTM said services will work as Paytm to expand its existing relationships with leading third-party banks to distribute payments and financial services products.

Chapters:
0:00 Intro
0:28 RBI Bans PayTM services
0:48 PayTM Business Timeline
1:40 PayTM One97 Communication Services
3:29 RBI Ban Rules Point Wise
4:20 PayTM Reply on RBI Ban
6:21 What to do if i'm using PayTM Services?

Queries Solved:
1) PayTM Ban in Details
2) PayTM Wallet Ban
3) PayTM Fast Tag Ban
4) PayTM QR Code, Soundbox, Payment Gateway (PG), All in one QR by PayTM will not work?
5) How To Redeem PayTM wallet or saving account amount to Bank account in hindi?
6) Redeem PayTM FasTag money in bank account?
7) RBI Ban on PayTM in Hindi
8) SidTalk by Siddhant Jain

snippet.title: Janaabe Jaaniya (Official Video) Gulraj Singh, Javed Ali | Ayaan Zubair, Riva Arora | Manoj Yadav
snippet.description:
VYRL Originals invites you to experience the first flush of childhood love with our latest "Janaabe Jaaniya". Sung by the popular singer Javed Ali, composed by Gulraj Singh & written by Manoj Yadav. Janaabe Jaaniya is sweet harkening ode to the excitement of the puppy love - two young hearts who cross paths to mark the start of an innocent  and beautiful relationship. The video features fresh popular faces - Riva Arora known for her work in Bollywood films & Ayyan Zubair - who is raking up the image of being a digital heartthrob. Watch the video where love and personal Achievement merge , through a song that is an ode to fresh puppy love.

Episode 3997: Sodhi Ke Naye Number
--------------------------------------------------------
Taarak persuades Anjali to prepare something sweet for him. Tapu Sena requests Gogi to treat them since his father bought a new car. Sodhi joyfully shares the news of getting a new number for his car with everyone in Gokuldham society while Madhavi asks Bhide if they can also buy a new car.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Life Without PARENTS - Family vs Toxic Relatives | Mom Dad IMPORTANCE | MyMissAnand
snippet.description:
Hello Friends ! Jo jaisa dikhta hai kabhi kabhi hota nahin hai. Have you ever imagined life without parents, main to sapne mein bhi aisa soch nahi sakti. Chalo dekhein kya hai woh jo mere yaani ki Shanaya ke sath hua ki saari duniya ulat plat hogayi.

Do Subscribe to my channel.

Also, OTHER CHANNELS: 
MissAnand Shorts: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCVoW...
CookWithNisha: https://www.youtube.com/c/CookWithNis...
Follow my Insta for BTS: https://tinyurl.com/MyMissAnand 
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/cookwithnisha/  
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/CookWithNisha/ 
YouTube Shorts: https://www.youtube.com/@Nishatops

NEW UPLOADS every FRIDAY @2:00 PM.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
Casting Credits: A S Productions: https://www.instagram.com/a.sproductioncasting
Leher
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
About MaaTri Media 

MaaTri, represents the most beautiful relationship between a mother and a daughter - Nisha Topwal & Anantya Anand aka. MyMissAnand. MaaTri is formed through a combination of two Hindi words - Maa (Mother) and PuTri (daughter) that brings forth energy, enthusiasm and determination to spread positive vibes through their outstanding content. Their content revolves around fashion, food, comedy, parenting, travel, glimpse of their family and simple day-to-day activities that both enjoy doing together. 
The duo captures a contemporary lifestyle of entrepreneur and food blogger mom and a teenage daughter and a social media influencer and shows how they both manage their work, school and personal life - simple pleasure of growing together, through engaging videos and fun visuals. Every post is curated and designed to make the audience laugh, learn, smile and entertain. 

#MyMissAnand #anantyaanand #momdad #lifewithoutyou #maabaap #relatives #maatrimedia #parents

snippet.title: Jharkhand CM बनते ही एक्शन में Champai Soren, पूर्व सीएम Hemant Soren के काम को लेकर कह दी बड़ी बात
snippet.description:
Jharkhand में सत्ता परिवर्तन होने के बाद Champai Soren ने अब Jharkhand की कमान संभाल ली है. CM बनते ही Champai Soren अब एक्शन मोड में आ गए हैं. मुख्यमंत्री बनते ही चंपई सोरेन ने Jharkhand Cabinet Meeting बुलाई. इस दौरान उन्होंने कैबिनेट की बैठक में कई बड़े फैसले लिए. कैबिनेट की बैठक में Rajeev Ranjan को Champai Soren सरकार में महाधिवक्ता बनाने पर मुहर लगी.

The age of late 20s early 30s come with a longing for a partner, let this rom-com (romantic comedy) make you giggle and smile. find out how Kriti (Played by Plabita Borthakur, known for her role in PK, Lipstick Under My Burkha, and Breathe: Into the Shadows) finds the one, the love of her life. would it be her best friend Jai (Played by Aaron Arjun Koul known for his role in The Price of Free, Baked and Independent Lens, and Mehr in @girliyapa's Who's Your Gynac ) ? Or a walking talking green flag Raghav (Played by Vishal Vashishtha, known for his role in Amazon MiniTV's Hustlers) she met from Jeevansaathi and went on a couple of dates with. Would Jai make it out of this "friend-zone"? Would Raghav get some clarity and answers?

snippet.title: The Art of Letting Go | Dr Vikas Divyakirti
snippet.description:
To follow on Instagram, visit: https://www.instagram.com/divyakirti.vikas


प्रिय साथियो,

24 जनवरी को मुझे दिल्ली विश्वविद्यालय के 'हंसराज कॉलेज’ द्वारा आयोजित सेमिनार में अपने विचार रखने का अवसर मिला। विषय था- ‘The art of Letting Go' अर्थात् "चिंताओ को अलविदा कैसे कहें?" 

मुझे लगता है कि हममें से ज़्यादातर लोगों के मन में यह दुविधा होती है। अगर यह विषय आपको अपने नज़दीक महसूस हो तो आप भी सुनिये। उम्मीद है कि इससे आपको कुछ उपयोगी सूत्र मिल सकेंगे। 

आपकी टिप्पणी का इंतज़ार रहेगा!

आभार,
विकास दिव्यकीर्ति

About* 
------------

               Yeh kahani hai ek sanyukt parivaar mai rehnewale Modi khaandaan ki. Izzatdaar, ameer aur naamcheen hone ke bawajud, ghar ke sanskaar aur sanskriti hain inka saccha dhan. Unke jethani ke bete, Jigar ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi ki behen, Raashi se joh hai bohot hi chaalaak aur nakhrel.

Iss ghar ko chalati hai choti bahu, Kokilaben jissey darte hain saare sadasya. Kokilaben ke bade bete, Ahem ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi se joh hai ek saaf dil ki siddhi saadhi, anpapdh ladki. Unke jethani ke bete, Jigar ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi ki behen, Raashi se joh hai bohot hi chaalaak aur nakhrel. 
              Raashi hamesha dikhati hai neecha Gopi ko aur karti hai uske liye mushkilen taiyaar. Par Gopi ka haath thama Kokilaben ne aur banaya ussey hoshiyaar. Iss saas-bahu ki jodi ne apne pyaar, dulaar aur balidaan se bandhe rakha hai Modi parivaar ko.

Where it all began! A single word that defines almost everything about him above all defines the love, respect& importance he gives to us and our relationship.

We never knew that the word would resonate with so many of you guys and would be a mantra to all of you. In fact we never thought of releasing the video, but decided to do it for the unconditional love you kept pouring. 🥺
